I guess this is related to: sqlalchemy/engine/base.py#get_schema_names this function is called doing saving process of this connection and it fails using query:  
SELECT nspname FROM pg_namespace WHERE nspname NOT LIKE 'pg_%' ORDER BY nspname; 
if i change query to: 
SELECT nspname FROM pg_namespace WHERE nspname NOT LIKE 'pg_%%' ORDER BY nspname;
as i understand this isn't superset problem...

